@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mvcxth(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.66) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.11)) * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.05) - 0.17))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.67) * (v0 + 0.55 + v1 + 0.48)) - wp.sin((v0 + 0.60 + v2 + 0.82)))
    tmp = 0.11
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp))
    v1 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.79 / v2 + 0.51)) - wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.85)))
    data[tid] = v0
